uk.ac.ebi.pride.utilities.data.controller
Interface DataAccessController

All Superinterfaces:
MetaDataAccess, MzGraphDataAccess, PeptideDataAccess, ProteinDataAccess, ProteinGroupDataAccess, QuantDataAccess
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDataAccessController, CachedDataAccessController, MzDataControllerImpl, MzIdentMLControllerImpl, MzMLControllerImpl, MzTabControllerImpl, MzXmlControllerImpl, PeakControllerImpl, PRIDEWebServiceDataAccessController, PrideXmlControllerImpl, ReferencedIdentificationController
public interface DataAccessController
extends MetaDataAccess, MzGraphDataAccess, ProteinDataAccess, ProteinGroupDataAccess, PeptideDataAccess, QuantDataAccess

DataAccessController is an aggregate interface for data access. It extends a list of interfaces, also added methods for accessing metadata. Setting the state of the data access controller.
